    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132700/extras/16e18cf9f514b6bfef04c82885503469.avif?t=1769620526\" width=840 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Oceanic Rails</strong> is a game about management, strategy and optimization, where each week counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Manage your team to grow your island, before the landlord gets you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Be in charge of your floating island in the middle of the ocean, with a weekly quota that continues getting harder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">A bad decision can collapse your whole system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Think ahead! Grow… or lose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Clicks help, but with an island that big you need a team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">With an island that big, doing everything alone is impossible! You need a team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Hire helpers and assign specific tasks to them:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> plant crops, process resources and finish orders while you focus on your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The bigger your island, the harder it is to keep everything running!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Handmade levels that introduce new systems and push you closer and closer to the limit.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Roguelike</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Always changing runs. How long can you last?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Sandbox</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Build, decorate and experiment without limits or pressure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The market changes every day! New merchants arrive, and the conditions are never the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Unlock upgrade cards with temporal benefits and synergies, that redefine your play style on each session.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132700/extras/6dcc38738c9816a2ee6d6a3c2a6cfd51.poster.avif?t=1769620526\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132700/extras/6dcc38738c9816a2ee6d6a3c2a6cfd51.webm?t=1769620526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132700/extras/6dcc38738c9816a2ee6d6a3c2a6cfd51.mp4?t=1769620526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Plan the best you can, and learn to adapt on the fly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Design supply chains assigning helpers to each stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Optimize routes, balance production times and decide when it’s best to reinvest to grow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132700/extras/f7b1112cb12861ac1ddc9be72aa17814.poster.avif?t=1769620526\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=840 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132700/extras/f7b1112cb12861ac1ddc9be72aa17814.webm?t=1769620526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132700/extras/f7b1112cb12861ac1ddc9be72aa17814.mp4?t=1769620526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The bigger the island, the more fragile your system will become!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Oceanic Rails will arrive in Early Access. Thanks for your support on this project from the early stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">We are planning to expand the game with:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Animals</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Flowers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Fishing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">More Production</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Bigger product trees</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">And more..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Each update will aim to improve and expand on the game, without losing the core focus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
